Simple web-based chat program in Clojure in under 100 lines of Clojure code.

http://alenribic.com/chat-100


DEPENDENCIES:
=============================

- Compojure (trunk / master)
- Clojure-contrib (trunk / master)


USAGE:
=============================

Run the following in REPL:

(ns chat-100)
(load-file "/path-to-chat-100-dir/chat-100.clj")

Open web browser and go to:

http://localhost:8080/chat


